              "text": "You see a dark shadow moving through the trees. You freeze, trying\nto get a better look at it. The shape seems humanoid, but taller than\nyou, with a slightly forward-sloping posture. It steps into the light for\na moment, and you catch a glimpse of a being covered in long fur.\nThen it steps behind a tree and vanishes. You hurry to the spot where\nyou last saw it but find nothing."
            }
